
!.env.example
# ====================================
# Bell Data Intelligence — git ignore
# Generated by Preview Branch Model.command
# IMPORTANT: leading slash anchors to repo root only. WITHOUT it, the pattern
# Leading slashes anchor these to the REPO ROOT so they don't accidentally
# Local config — API keys go in macOS Keychain, NOT here, but ignore just in case.
# Local env files NEVER go to git. Use Railway env vars in production.
# Local-only command outputs / temp files
# Local-only data, secrets, and build artifacts. None of this belongs on GitHub.
# Marketing site Mapbox token if accidentally written to file (it should be env)
# Run logs from local Portal sessions
# Scratch / throwaway test scripts (e.g. harvester self-tests)
# The Data/ folder holds raw scraper output (millions of records). Not for git.
# also matched Portal/server/config/ and silently excluded plans.js (the
# bug we hit on 2026-05-27).
# match nested folders with the same name (e.g. Portal/server/config/).
# ─── Bell local-only data (huge + sensitive) ───────────────────────────────
# ─── Env files (secrets) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ─── Misc ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ─── Next.js ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ─── Node ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ─── Postgres dumps / backups ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# ─── macOS / OS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.DS_Store
**/.mapbox-token
**/.next/
**/Config/local/
**/Config/secrets/
**# The Data/ folder holds raw scraper OUTPUT (millions of records) — never in git.
# But the scraper CODE is versioned (carved in 2026-07-23) so both machines stay in
# sync via git and the ROG's nightly self-update covers the scrapers too. Pattern:
# ignore everything under Data/, then re-open ONLY the code directories, then
# re-ignore their output/junk. Git cannot re-include inside an excluded DIRECTORY,
# hence the level-by-level dance.
/Data/*
!/Data/Companies/
/Data/Companies/*
!/Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/
/Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/*
!/Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/Directories/
!/Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/Other Sources/
Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/**/scans/
Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/**/__pycache__/
Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/**/node_modules/
Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/**/venv/
Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/**/.venv/
Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/**/State/
Data/Companies/1. Data Gathering/**/state/raw/
**/Data/scans/
**/Operations/credits/
**/Operations/enrichment_queue/
**/Operations/run_logs/
**/_*.mjs
**/node_modules/
**/out/
